Interface Authenticator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicAuthenticator, BearerTokenAuthenticator, CloudPakForDataAuthenticator, IamAuthenticator, NoAuthAuthenticator, TokenRequestBasedAuthenticator

    public interface Authenticator
    This interface defines the common methods and constants associated with an Authenticator implementation.
